        "content": "<p>fitzgen created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12923#discussion_r3022714705\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Maybe define a constant at the top of the file, rather than open-coding <code>4</code> here</p>\n</blockquote>",
