    {
        "content": "<p>fitzgen created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12923#discussion_r3023541516\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Ditto regarding matching on a random int to choose which field to mutate vs registering multiple mutation candidates by calling <code>.mutate(...)</code> on each field.</p>\n<p>And I think we could <code>derive(Mutate)</code> on <code>ExceptionOps</code> too.</p>\n<p>Probably can just derive on all the \"AST\" types, honestly, and then just let <code>fixup</code> clean up the limits and such.</p>\n</blockquote>",
